sequenceDiagram
    actor Participant
    participant MAW as «view»<br>:MyActivitiesWindow
    participant VAW as «view»<br>:VolunteerApplyWindow
    participant VAC as «controller»<br>:VolunteerApplicationController
    participant VA as VolunteerApplication

    note over Participant,VA: USE CASE 1: APPLY VOLUNTEER
    Participant->>+VAW: fill skills, notes & submit
    VAW->>+VAC: store(request)
    VAC->>+VA: create application
    VA-->>-VAC: application saved
    VAC-->>-VAW: return redirect
    VAW-->>-Participant: display apply success message

    note over Participant,VA: USE CASE 2: VIEW APPLICATION
    Participant->>+MAW: click to view application details
    MAW->>+VAC: show(id)
    VAC->>+VA: get application details
    VA-->>-VAC: return application data
    VAC-->>-MAW: return view with data
    MAW-->>-Participant: display application details

    note over Participant,VA: USE CASE 3: EDIT APPLICATION
    Participant->>+VAW: modify application details & submit
    VAW->>+VAC: update(request, id)
    VAC->>+VA: update application data
    VA-->>-VAC: update confirmed
    VAC-->>-MAW: return redirect
    MAW-->>-Participant: display updated application

    note over Participant,VA: USE CASE 4: CANCEL APPLICATION
    Participant->>+MAW: click cancel application
    MAW->>+VAC: destroy(request, id)
    
    alt [applicationStatus=pending]
        VAC->>+VA: deleteApplication(id)
        VA-->>-VAC: record deleted
        VAC-->>-MAW: return success redirect
        MAW-->>-Participant: display cancellation confirmed
    else [applicationStatus!=pending]
        VAC-->>MAW: return error redirect
        MAW-->>Participant: display cannot cancel approved/declined application
    end
